Reasoning: The paper deals with MIMO signaling and analysis of linear precoding techniques. cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category as it deals with the fundamental limits of communication systems. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SI (Signal Processing) are also likely categories as they deal with the design and analysis of communication systems. cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are less likely categories but still relevant as they deal with the design and analysis of systems.
